hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again-0&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=e088b9d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/restore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again-0</a><br />\n🧐🧐【元朗黑夜連登獨立調查委員會】🧐🧐<br />\n🎊 On <strong>July 23, 2019</strong>：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/34AmN69rRScNafEC9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F34AmN69rRScNafEC9&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=25824c3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/34AmN69rRScNafEC9</a><br />\n🙏🙏所有香港大學學生、舊生以及職員參與聯署，要求香港大學校長張翔履行社會使命。🙏🙏<a href=\"https://forms.gle/UAVikwsyCmdDEyy76\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FUAVikwsyCmdDEyy76&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=c11d5051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/UAVikwsyCmdDEyy76</a><br />\n🤭我唔捨得何君堯去美國🤭<br />\n🥳大家快聯署留底佢全家🥳<br />\n🎊 On <strong>July 21, 2019</strong>：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/make-junius-ho-kwan-yiu-and-his-immediate-family-members-ineligible-us-entry-citizenship-and-visas?fbclid=IwAR0fZRhrobDg_hxUKcYKAN0XV833ZjHwxWu4XY82PzypubZpwq4ToZ8-e7M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fmake-junius-ho-kwan-yiu-and-his-immediate-family-members-ineligible-us-entry-citizenship-and-visas%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0fZRhrobDg_hxUKcYKAN0XV833ZjHwxWu4XY82PzypubZpwq4ToZ8-e7M&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=053ab077\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/make-junius-ho-kwan-yiu-and-his-immediate-family-members-ineligible-us-entry-citizenship-and-visas?fbclid=IwAR0fZRhrobDg_hxUKcYKAN0XV833ZjHwxWu4XY82PzypubZpwq4ToZ8-e7M</a><br />\n🥰🤩[遍地攬炒] 一人一信幫何君堯律師世世代代享受大灣區榮耀🥰🤩😁內含教學😁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351572</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻<br />\n🥳724 港鐵不合作運動 時間:上午七時半<br />\n🥳725 休息一天 (有待更新)<br />\n🥳726 機場集會 時間: 下午一時至下午十一時五十九分*不反對通知書申請中*<br />\n🥳727 光復元朗 時間: 下午四時<br />\n😎建議遊行提早於😎上午十時至中午十二時期間開始😎以確保安全😎<br />\n請各位努力推po以提出遊行時間修訂<br />\n已取消或延期:<br />\n原定728 港島西遊行&nbsp;取消<br />\n原定728 將軍澳遊戲&nbsp;日期待定<br />\n原定728 紅磡、土瓜灣遊行&nbsp;改期至817<br />\n兩條戰線同樣重要 但係請各位心水清&nbsp;<br />\n任何一方都不能忽視 以防誤中港共圈套<br />\n亦避免被各方妖孽分散注意力 必須將火力對準政權<br />\n政府務必回應五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n😡😡😡😡😡😡😡😡😡😡<br />\n銀行商店拉閘「靜過十號波」<br />\n指揮官拍膊與黑幫論形勢<br />\n大狀：必須獨立調查<br />\n警遲到場：睇唔到錶<br />\n999無人聽 市民向消防求救<br />\n「飛天南」蘇醒 稱被打無傷痕<br />\n林鄭重國徽輕視港人安危<br />\n記者叫特首「講返句人話」<br />\n王志民自誇中聯辦巍然不動<br />\n建制派反指示威者「挑機」<br />\n總商會轉軚促撤法：失職官員須問責<br />\n何君堯飯局 惡煞食飽打人<br />\n百人毀議辦 轟何勾結黑幫<br />\n被指撬閘 元朗區會副主席辯稱勸交<br />\n賴上環清場 盧偉聰：調配人手需時<br />\n元朗黑夜 還原白色恐襲8小時<br />\n休班紀律部隊自發趕到救人<br />\n搵仔媽媽︰警無資格𢭃人工<br />\n少年痛哭元朗沉淪<br />\n眾志成員遇襲傷頭<br />\n林卓廷轟建制無恥<br />\n青年護花慘遭狂鞭<br />\n柳俊江義載變血人<br />\n居民攜衫救人被毆<br />\n三區讓路 7.27「光復元朗」<br />\n巿民港鐵內受傷可索償<br />\n遇襲記者︰好似屍殺列車<br />\n不滿警黑合作 民政局職員疑罷工<br />\n國際將香港新疆相提並論<br />\n台灣不再信一國兩制謊言<br />\n警再開槍射頭 示威者重創<br />\n記者遭速龍舉槍棍指嚇<br />\n濃煙下槍聲四起 示威者變活靶<br />\n警不作為 黑幫肆虐元、屯、荃 變死城"},{"pid":"cee9cb2ad8c289e2be8b9c6c46ef6d7e3e32726d","tid":1355633,"uid":152861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:33:03.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"c1c19a0b56bfae0541d6b9aba8ab997b805729d4","tid":1355633,"uid":106164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:37:46.000Z","msg":"要逼到啲9交代開槍"},{"pid":"75e32079bc07d02173ae29b5275595caefda9e8b","tid":1355633,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:38:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9f7c33b5071c79813e4a91c8001572593fad91d","tid":1355633,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:39:39.000Z","msg":"兩邊都要追究<br />\n<br />\n警察一方面開槍打人<br />\n一方面縱容鄉黑打人<br />\n<br />\n兩件事根本殊途同歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f572d8747311132bdd84397704a9c2edf230bab","tid"